<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>UFC president Dana White has revealed that his foray into the boxing world will be detailed in the next couple of weeks. </p>

<p>White has been weighing up a move into the sport for some time and the legendary MMA promoter is on the brink of a major announcement. </p>

<p>He told BT Sport: 'The world of boxing hasn't been able to do what I've been able to do [in MMA] over the last 20 years.</p>

<p>Dana White has teased an announcement about his move into the world of boxing </p>

<p>'If they can't do things when the world is normal, you can't expect them to do things when the world is crazy.</p>

<p>'I peeked under the hood a lot there for the last year. Looked at different things and I said, "I don't know man, I don't know if this is fixable".'</p>

<p>He added: 'Funnily enough, since the pandemic I've been looking at other options too.</p>

<p>'And we'll probably have something to announce here soon. Yeah [it is in the world of boxing].</p>

<p>White, pictured here alongside Floyd Mayweather, said he's 'peeked under the hood of boxing'</p>

<p>White gave an interview outlining what he had been doing to study the boxing world </p>

<p>'When it's time, I'll let you know, I'm not ready yet. But [it'll be] in the next couple of weeks.'   </p>

<p>I remains to be seen whether White will work with a stable of boxers or have more grand ambitions for changing the convoluted way the sport is run. </p>

<p>White has been a key part of the UFC's success over the years and the growth of MMA into a legitimate sport sanctioned all over the United States.   </p>

<p>He orchestrated the move to Fight Island in Abu Dhabi to put on a number of huge events during the coronavirus pandemic as a grand contingency plan.   </p>

<p>UFC 253 on Yas Island takes place this Saturday and will be headlined by Israel Adesanya vs Paulo Costa.  </p>

<p>Israel Adesanya will be taking on Paulo Costa in a middleweight title fight this weekend</p>
